some of the western provinces , such as shaanxi and sichuan , are relatively strong in science and technology and have a fairly large number of scientific and technological achievements .
the question at present is to translate scientific and technological achievements into real productive forces , translate laboratory superiority into productive superiority , translate product superiority into market superiority , translate market superiority into superiority for better returns , and translate domestic superiority into international superiority .
exchange resources for capital , raise funds for development .
a key problem for developing the west is insufficient funds .
viewed from the current situation , greater government investment is necessary but has little potential , also it does not conform to what is demanded by the law of market economy if we totally rely on government investment .
hence , local fund - raising is the principal way .
but due to economic backwardness , capital accumulation is so slow that it is difficult to meet the demand for rapid development .
the west is rich in resources ; swapping resources for capital and technology is a key option .
for example , in such respects as land utilization , resources exploitation , efforts should be made to offer investors with preferential terms , in a bid to attract investors from other parts of the nation and from foreign countries .
in this way , it will of course bring losses to the local economies .
but no policy measure can possibly be perfect ; as long as the gains are greater than the losses and the advantages outweigh the disadvantages , then it can be taken .
whether we are talking about the economic development of the west or of the whole nation , the advantages of speeding up the development of the west by exchanging resources for capital and technology certainly outweigh the disadvantages .
give stronger financial support to development of the west .
finance is the nucleus of a modern economy .
to develop the economy of the west , we must pay full attention to the financial market and make use of it .
