the report also pointed out : moreover , some eu member states are , in fact , not eager to let china enter the wto .
if china stays outside the wto a little longer , this will naturally ease the pressure on the eu for competition .
against this broad background , it is just a matter of time for the eu and china to reach an agreement in their negotiations on china 's wto entry . "
