only thus , can we realize the sustainable development .
during the 21st century , we should continue to exert efforts to grasp the work of keeping a low birth rate , and rationally using and strictly managing resources in order to protect and create a good ecological environment .
the whole party and the whole nation from the leadership to the masses should be determined to realize the established population , resources and environment objectives so as to guarantee the realization of the grand objective of china 's cross - century development .
