we should strengthen the building of ranks of workers to take charge of the work on population , resources and environment , and strive to raise the quality of the work on population , resources and environment in the grass roots .
the party and government principal leaders should coordinate the work and organize the efforts of all sectors to comprehensively tackle the population , resources and environmental problems .
