violations of the law should be called to account in line with law and those acts that constitute a crime should be punished and dealt with according to law .
the party committees and governments at all levels should manage things strictly in line with the law , policies and plans .
party - member cadres , especially leading cadres , should serve as examples in carrying out family planning as well as in protecting resources and environment .
we should uphold the operating principle of believing in , relying on , respecting and serving the masses .
in doing our work , we must guard against bureaucracy , dogmatism , and formalism .
mass organizations such as the trade union , communist youth league , women 's federation , and family planning association should give full play to their role , and jointly promote the work on population , resources , and environment .
